    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for early intentional scribbling', 'Crayola MyFirst Jumbo Crayons - Assorted Colours (Pack of 8)', 'Crayola', 'Amazon UK', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/CRAYOLA-MyFirst-Coloring-Toddlers-Multicolored/dp/B00BUIE8OU', NULL, '£3.94', 'in_stock', '12+ Months', 'Easy-grip jumbo crayons designed for toddlers to make their first marks and explore colors. Less breakable and non-toxic.', 'These crayons are excellent for toddlers just past two and a half, supporting their growing fine motor control for intentional mark-making. Their chunky size prevents frustration, and while not explicitly washable, they clean up easily from surfaces. A great starting point for budding artists.', 'The jumbo size and easy grip are perfect for developing fine motor skills at 31-33 months, encouraging intentional scribbling and early shape-making, a clear stage shift from earlier fitting/matching activities.', 'Not explicitly washable, so supervision is recommended for younger toddlers prone to coloring off-paper.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.amazon.co.uk/CRAYOLA-MyFirst-Coloring-Toddlers-Multicolored/dp/B00BUIE8OU', 'https://www.thebump.com/a/crayons-for-toddlers']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for mess-free creativity', 'Crayola Ultra Clean Large Washable Crayons', 'Crayola', 'Mother & Baby (Amazon UK)', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Crayola-Ultra-Clean-Washable-Crayons/dp/B00K44458S', NULL, '£5.99', 'in_stock', '3+', 'Large, washable crayons that easily clean from skin, clothing, and painted walls. Perfect for mess-free creative play.', 'For parents who value easy cleanup, these washable crayons are a lifesaver. At 31-33 months, toddlers are gaining more control but still prone to accidental marks, making the ''Ultra Clean'' feature highly appealing. The larger size is comfortable for their developing grip, encouraging confident mark-making.', 'The washable feature directly addresses a common parental concern at this age, allowing toddlers to explore intentional mark-making freely without fear of permanent messes. The large size supports their developing grip for clearer turns and early shape-making.', 'May be slightly less vibrant than non-washable counterparts, but the convenience often outweighs this for parents.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned, especially for parents concerned about mess.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.motherandbaby.com/reviews/toddler-toys/crayons-for-toddlers/', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Crayola-Ultra-Clean-Washable-Crayons/dp/B00K44458S']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for developing fine motor skills', 'Happy Triangles Jumbo Crayons 12 Pack', 'Happy Triangles', 'Hobbycraft', 'https://www.hobbycraft.co.uk/happy-triangles-jumbo-crayons-12-pack/6314011000.html', NULL, '£5.00', 'in_stock', 'Not specified, but ''jumbo'' and ''triangular'' suggest toddler-friendly', 'Triangular jumbo crayons designed for small hands, promoting motor skills and comfortable grip. Less prone to breaking.', 'The triangular shape of these crayons is a fantastic feature for 31-33 month olds, as it naturally encourages a more mature pencil grip. This supports the stage shift towards more controlled and intentional drawing, helping toddlers refine their fine motor skills without frustration.', 'The triangular shape is key for encouraging a tripod grip, a significant developmental step at this age for more precise mark-making and early shape formation. This directly aligns with the ''My hands can make more now'' cluster.', 'May not be as widely available as Crayola, so check stock. Washability not specified.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned, particularly for encouraging proper grip.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.hobbycraft.co.uk/happy-triangles-jumbo-crayons-12-pack/6314011000.html', 'https://www.thebump.com/a/crayons-for-toddlers']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 4, 4, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for expansive creative play', 'MÅLA Drawing paper roll, 30 m', 'IKEA', 'IKEA', 'https://www.ikea.com/gb/en/p/mala-drawing-paper-roll-70461088/', NULL, '£3.50', 'in_stock', 'Not specified, but suitable for children', 'A large, 30-meter roll of drawing paper, perfect for expansive creative projects and encouraging big movements.', 'This large paper roll is ideal for 31-33 month olds who are ready to make bigger, more intentional marks. It provides ample space for them to explore their creativity without being confined to small pages, encouraging gross motor skills alongside fine motor development. It''s a versatile canvas for all their scribbles and early shapes.', 'The large format directly supports the stage shift towards intentional mark-making and early shape-making by providing an unconstrained canvas. It allows for bigger, more confident movements than smaller paper, fostering a sense of control and purpose.', 'Requires a flat surface or easel for best use. Can be used with various art supplies.', 'buy', true, 'A practical and inspiring gift for any budding artist.', 'A good staple to have for creative play. Consider if the family already has a similar large paper option.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.ikea.com/gb/en/p/mala-drawing-paper-roll-70461088/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for vibrant, smooth coloring', 'Honeysticks 100% Pure Beeswax Crayons (Jumbo)', 'Honeysticks', 'Mother & Baby (Amazon UK)', 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Honeysticks-100-Pure-Beeswax-Crayons/dp/B01I2GNSWU', NULL, '£18.95', 'in_stock', '12+ Months', 'Natural, non-toxic jumbo beeswax crayons with a smooth, vibrant laydown. Perfect for little hands and safe for curious toddlers.', 'Honeysticks offer a premium, natural option for 31-33 month olds. Their smooth texture allows for effortless, vibrant mark-making, which is highly encouraging for toddlers developing intentional drawing skills. The jumbo size is easy to hold, and the pure beeswax composition provides peace of mind for parents of toddlers who still explore with their mouths.', 'The smooth glide and vibrant colors encourage confident and intentional mark-making, aligning with the stage shift. The natural, non-toxic material is a key benefit for this age group, where oral exploration is still common.', 'Higher price point than traditional wax crayons. Limited color palette in smaller packs.', 'buy', true, 'A high-quality, natural gift option for discerning parents.', 'High chance the family owns a version already. Look for the stage shift: a version that adds clearer turns, richer pretend play, more control or easier setup rather than simply more of the same.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.amazon.co.uk/Honeysticks-100-Pure-Beeswax-Crayons/dp/B01I2GNSWU', 'https://www.motherandbaby.com/reviews/toddler-toys/crayons-for-toddlers/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 6, 6, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for budgets', 'Crayola Jumbo Crayons 24 Pack', 'Crayola', NULL, 'https://www.hobbycraft.co.uk/crayola-jumbo-crayons-24-pack/5630911000.html', NULL, '£4.00', NULL, NULL, 'Crayola — Crayola Jumbo Crayons 24 Pack', 'Good value pack of chunky crayons, suitable for developing grip and early drawing skills.', 'Good value pack of chunky crayons, suitable for developing grip and early drawing skills.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 7, 7, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for small spaces', 'Crayola Twistables Colouring Crayons (12 Pack)', 'Crayola', NULL, 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/Crayola-Twistables-Colouring-Crayons-Pack/dp/B00004T8E0', NULL, '£3.99', NULL, NULL, 'Crayola — Crayola Twistables Colouring Crayons (12 Pack)', 'Twist-up mechanism eliminates sharpening, good for children who break traditional crayons easily.', 'Twist-up mechanism eliminates sharpening, good for children who break traditional crayons easily.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_chunky_crayons_and_big_paper', 8, 8, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for borrowing first', 'abeec 144 Wax Crayons', 'abeec', NULL, 'https://www.amazon.co.uk/abeec-Crayons-Assorted-Colours-Children/dp/B07L2W7X7Q', NULL, '£14.99', NULL, NULL, 'abeec — abeec 144 Wax Crayons', 'Bulk pack offers great value for frequent use or multiple children, with chunky grip.', 'Bulk pack offers great value for frequent use or multiple children, with chunky grip.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
