    ('cat_hoops_beanbags_and_jump_markers', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for comprehensive gross motor play', 'Jump-In Hoops & Bean Bags (part of The Researcher Play Kit)', 'Lovevery', 'Lovevery UK', 'https://lovevery.co.uk/products/the-play-kits-the-researcher', NULL, '£120.00', 'in_stock', '31-33 months', 'Part of a play kit, these hoops and bean bags encourage hopping, tossing, and jumping for gross motor development.', 'This set is perfectly aligned with the 31-33 month stage, encouraging deliberate movement and coordination. It''s a high-quality, well-researched option for parents seeking a comprehensive approach to play. Consider borrowing or holding off if you already have similar items or are on a budget, as it''s part of a larger kit.', 'The hoops and bean bags encourage deliberate aiming and jumping, directly supporting the ''balance and bravery'' cluster and the stage shift towards targeted movement at 31-33m.', 'Only available as part of ''The Researcher Play Kit'', not sold separately. Higher price point due to being part of a larger kit.', 'buy', true, 'A thoughtful gift if the family is already invested in the Lovevery system or values high-quality, age-specific play kits.', 'Check if the family already has a Lovevery subscription or similar high-quality gross motor play items.', NULL, 'strong', ARRAY['https://lovevery.co.uk/products/the-play-kits-the-researcher']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_hoops_beanbags_and_jump_markers', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for versatile indoor and outdoor play', 'Plastic Hula Hoop Set (45.7cm)', 'Early Years Resources', 'Early Years Resources', 'https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/plastic-hula-hoop-set/', NULL, '£12.60', 'in_stock', 'Early Years setting', 'A set of four durable plastic hula hoops in different colours, suitable for various active play activities.', 'These hula hoops are a classic for a reason, offering endless possibilities for active play, from target games to jumping. The smaller size is ideal for 31-33 month olds to manipulate and control, supporting their developing coordination. A great ''buy'' for encouraging independent and imaginative movement.', 'Supports the stage shift by providing a versatile tool for deliberate movement, aiming, and jumping, encouraging creative play with rules and targets.', 'No specific toddler age range, but ''Early Years setting'' implies suitability. No customer reviews available on the product page.', 'buy', true, 'A practical and fun gift that encourages physical activity and imaginative play.', 'A good basic set; consider upgrading only if a more specialized or durable set is needed.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/plastic-hula-hoop-set/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_hoops_beanbags_and_jump_markers', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for developing throwing and aiming skills', 'Play Bean Bags Pack Of 4', 'Early Years Resources', 'Early Years Resources', 'https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/pe-sport/pe/bean-bags/', NULL, '£5.40', 'in_stock', 'Early Years setting', 'A pack of four colourful bean bags, ideal for throwing, catching, and target games to develop coordination.', 'These bean bags are perfect for the 31-33 month old who is refining their throwing and aiming skills. They encourage deliberate actions and can be used in a variety of games, supporting the ''balance and bravery'' cluster. A definite ''buy'' for active play.', 'Directly supports the stage shift by providing a soft, safe object for deliberate throwing and aiming games, fostering coordination and control.', 'No specific toddler age range, but ''Early Years setting'' implies suitability. No customer reviews available on the product page.', 'buy', true, 'A simple yet effective gift that promotes active play and skill development.', 'These are a good basic set. Consider if a themed or more durable set is preferred.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.earlyyearsresources.co.uk/pe-sport/pe/bean-bags/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_hoops_beanbags_and_jump_markers', 4, 4, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for creating defined play areas', 'Sequencing Floor Marker Spots (Pack of 6)', 'TTS Group', 'TTS Group', 'https://www.tts-group.co.uk/sequencing-floor-marker-spots/1008428.html', NULL, '£13.99', 'in_stock', NULL, 'A pack of multicoloured, durable vinyl spots for effective movement control and positional instruction in games.', 'These floor markers are excellent for defining play areas, creating targets for throwing, or marking spots for jumping. They support the development of spatial awareness and following instructions, crucial for 31-33 month olds. A ''buy'' for structured active play.', 'Facilitates the stage shift by providing clear visual cues for deliberate jumping, aiming, and movement patterns, encouraging rule-based play.', 'No explicit age guidance, but suitable for early years. No customer reviews available on the product page.', 'buy', true, 'A practical gift for encouraging organized active play and skill development.', 'These are a good foundational item for active play. Consider if more themed or interactive markers are desired.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://www.tts-group.co.uk/sequencing-floor-marker-spots/1008428.html']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_hoops_beanbags_and_jump_markers', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for basic, durable hoops', 'Deluxe Hoop (60cm)', 'Bishop', 'Bishopsport', 'https://bishopsport.co.uk/products/se1010_p_deluxe-hoop', NULL, '£6.00', 'in_stock', NULL, 'A durable, basic plastic hoop, ideal for a variety of active games and physical development activities.', 'This basic, durable hoop is a versatile tool for encouraging gross motor skills at 31-33 months. It can be used for jumping through, aiming at, or creating simple obstacle courses, aligning with the ''balance and bravery'' cluster. A solid ''buy'' for its simplicity and open-ended play potential.', 'Supports the stage shift by offering a fundamental tool for deliberate movement, jumping, and aiming, fostering creativity in active play.', 'No explicit age guidance, but suitable for early years. No customer reviews available on the product page.', 'buy', true, 'A classic and versatile gift that encourages physical activity.', 'A good foundational hoop. Consider if a set with multiple sizes or colours is preferred.', NULL, 'good', ARRAY['https://bishopsport.co.uk/products/se1010_p_deluxe-hoop']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_hoops_beanbags_and_jump_markers', 6, 6, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for budgets', 'Bucket of 12 Assorted Original Bean Bags', 'M3C Sports', NULL, 'https://www.m3csports.com/primary-play-bean-bags-hoops.html', NULL, '£11.65', NULL, NULL, 'M3C Sports — Bucket of 12 Assorted Original Bean Bags', 'Good value for a bulk pack of bean bags, suitable for throwing and aiming games. Similar to a Top Pick but less detailed product information and no specific age guidance.', 'Good value for a bulk pack of bean bags, suitable for throwing and aiming games. Similar to a Top Pick but less detailed product information and no specific age guidance.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
