    ('cat_picture_books_with_little_stories', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for learning days and counting', 'The Very Hungry Caterpillar', 'Eric Carle', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A caterpillar eats through many foods, then transforms into a butterfly.', 'This classic book is perfect for 31-33 month olds, offering a clear sequence of events as the caterpillar eats through different foods each day. Children can easily predict what comes next, reinforcing early sequencing skills. It also introduces counting and the days of the week in a gentle, engaging way. Borrow if already owned, otherwise buy.', 'This classic book is perfect for 31-33 month olds, offering a clear sequence of events as the caterpillar eats through different foods each day. Children can easily predict what comes next, reinforcing early sequencing skills. It also introduces counting and the days of the week in a gentle, engaging way. Borrow if already owned, otherwise buy.', NULL, 'buy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'strong', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_url'),
    ('cat_picture_books_with_little_stories', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for interactive animal discovery', 'Dear Zoo', 'Rod Campbell', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A child writes to the zoo for a pet, receiving various animals with lift-the-flaps.', '‘Dear Zoo’ is an ideal pick for this age band, with its interactive lift-the-flap format encouraging children to predict which animal will be revealed next. The repetitive text and clear sequence of unsuitable pets before finding the perfect one strongly support the ‘asking what happens next’ cluster. Buy for a new experience, or bring back out if it’s been a while.', '‘Dear Zoo’ is an ideal pick for this age band, with its interactive lift-the-flap format encouraging children to predict which animal will be revealed next. The repetitive text and clear sequence of unsuitable pets before finding the perfect one strongly support the ‘asking what happens next’ cluster. Buy for a new experience, or bring back out if it’s been a while.', NULL, 'buy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'strong', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_url'),
    ('cat_picture_books_with_little_stories', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for peek-a-boo fun', 'Where’s Mr Lion?', 'Nosy Crow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A felt-flap book where children search for hidden animals, ending with a mirror.', 'This interactive felt-flap book is excellent for developing prediction skills as children guess which animal is hiding. The simple narrative and engaging peek-a-boo elements align perfectly with the ‘asking what happens next’ cluster, providing satisfying reveals. Buy for a new, engaging experience.', 'This interactive felt-flap book is excellent for developing prediction skills as children guess which animal is hiding. The simple narrative and engaging peek-a-boo elements align perfectly with the ‘asking what happens next’ cluster, providing satisfying reveals. Buy for a new, engaging experience.', NULL, 'buy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'strong', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_url'),
    ('cat_picture_books_with_little_stories', 4, 4, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for learning daily routines', 'How to Brush Your Teeth with Snappy Croc', 'Jane Clarke & Georgie Birkett', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'A fun, rhyming story teaching children the step-by-step process of brushing teeth.', 'This book excels at teaching a practical life skill through a clear, step-by-step sequence, making it highly relevant for the 31-33 month age band. The predictable progression of brushing teeth helps children understand and anticipate each action, fostering early problem-solving and routine comprehension. Buy for a practical and engaging read.', 'This book excels at teaching a practical life skill through a clear, step-by-step sequence, making it highly relevant for the 31-33 month age band. The predictable progression of brushing teeth helps children understand and anticipate each action, fostering early problem-solving and routine comprehension. Buy for a practical and engaging read.', NULL, 'buy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'strong', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_url'),
    ('cat_picture_books_with_little_stories', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for sing-along animal sounds', 'Old Macdonald Had a Farm', 'Camilla Reid', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'An interactive counting book with slide buttons featuring farm animals and their sounds.', 'This interactive book, based on a familiar nursery rhyme, is perfect for encouraging prediction and sequencing through its repetitive structure and animal sounds. Children can anticipate the next animal and its sound, making it a highly engaging and educational experience for this age group. Buy for a lively, interactive story time.', 'This interactive book, based on a familiar nursery rhyme, is perfect for encouraging prediction and sequencing through its repetitive structure and animal sounds. Children can anticipate the next animal and its sound, making it a highly engaging and educational experience for this age group. Buy for a lively, interactive story time.', NULL, 'buy', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'strong', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_url'),
