    ('cat_pouring_cups_and_water_lab', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for budding scientists', 'Splashology!™ Water Lab', 'Learning Resources', 'Learning Resources UK', 'https://www.learningresources.co.uk/splashology-water-lab', NULL, '£27.95', 'in_stock', 'Ages 3+', 'A water science kit with tools for hands-on experiments, teaching volume, buoyancy, and water flow.', 'This water lab is perfect for 31-33 month olds ready for more purposeful water experimentation. It encourages understanding of cause and effect through engaging activities. Consider borrowing if unsure about sustained interest.', 'The Splashology! Water Lab directly addresses the stage shift by providing multiple tools for experimentation, fostering understanding of volume, buoyancy, and water flow, and encouraging cause-and-effect play. The included experiment cards guide purposeful exploration.', 'Contains small parts, requiring close adult supervision for children under 3 years old.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'Check whether the family already has a basic version. Upgrade only if this version solves a new job for 31-33 months.', 'Use only with close adult supervision around water. CHOKING HAZARD! Small parts. Not for children under 3 yrs.', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.learningresources.co.uk/splashology-water-lab']::text[], 'check_age_fit'),
    ('cat_pouring_cups_and_water_lab', 2, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for engaging bath time play', 'Spin ''N'' Sprinkle Water Lab', 'Yookidoo', 'Yookidoo UK', 'https://uk.yookidoo.com/products/spin-n-sprinkle', NULL, '£14.99', 'in_stock', '1-3 Years', 'A bath toy creating a chain reaction of water sprays, with a test tube, funnels, and spinning elements.', 'This water lab is fantastic for encouraging cause-and-effect understanding and fine motor skills during bath time. It''s a great option for 31-33 month olds who enjoy interactive water play. A good ''buy'' for a unique bath toy.', 'The Spin ''N'' Sprinkle Water Lab provides an engaging way for toddlers to experiment with water flow, cause and effect, and basic measurement (with the test tube''s marks). Its interactive nature aligns well with purposeful experimentation at this age.', 'Primarily a bath toy, so may not be suitable for wider water table play without adaptation.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'Check whether the family already has a basic version. Upgrade only if this version solves a new job for 31-33 months.', 'Use only with close adult supervision around water.', 'good', ARRAY['https://uk.yookidoo.com/products/spin-n-sprinkle']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_pouring_cups_and_water_lab', 3, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for versatile outdoor exploration', 'Little Tikes Bluey Bushlands Adventures Folding Water Tray', 'Little Tikes', 'Adventure Toys UK', 'https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/little-tikes-bluey-bushlands-adventures-folding-water-tray/', NULL, '£89.99', 'in_stock', 'Age 2+', 'A large folding water tray with a log ride, water wheel, lock gates, and character floats for imaginative water play.', 'This water tray offers extensive opportunities for purposeful water experimentation and imaginative play for 31-33 month olds. The various features like the water wheel and lock gates support cause-and-effect learning. A great ''buy'' for sustained outdoor engagement.', 'This large water tray provides multiple stations for pouring, flowing, and manipulating water, directly supporting the ''purposeful pouring and water experimentation'' aspect of the stage shift. The various features encourage cause-and-effect understanding and comparison of water movement.', 'Requires significant space for setup and storage. Higher price point.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'Check whether the family already has a basic version. Upgrade only if this version solves a new job for 31-33 months.', 'Use only with close adult supervision around water.', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/little-tikes-bluey-bushlands-adventures-folding-water-tray/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_pouring_cups_and_water_lab', 4, 4, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for simple, open-ended pouring', 'Scrunch Water Measure Snail', 'Scrunch', 'Adventure Toys UK', 'https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/scrunch-water-measure-snail/', NULL, '£6.99', 'in_stock', 'Age 1+', 'A collapsible silicone measuring cup (200ml) with internal marks, designed for pouring, measuring, and containing liquids.', 'This simple, yet effective, measuring snail is ideal for 31-33 month olds to practice precise pouring and early measurement concepts. Its collapsible design makes it practical for travel and storage. A definite ''buy'' for its versatility.', 'The Scrunch Water Measure Snail directly supports purposeful pouring and introduces early measurement concepts with its internal markings. Its stable base and easy-to-handle design make it suitable for toddlers refining their pouring skills.', 'May be too simple for children seeking more complex water play setups.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'Check whether the family already has a basic version. Upgrade only if this version solves a new job for 31-33 months.', 'None specified.', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/scrunch-water-measure-snail/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_pouring_cups_and_water_lab', 5, 5, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for imaginative water play', 'Little Tikes Bluey Beach Day Sand and Water Table', 'Little Tikes', 'Adventure Toys UK', 'https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/little-tikes-bluey-beach-day-sand-and-water-table/', NULL, '£59.99', 'in_stock', 'Age 1+', 'A Bluey-themed sand and water table with a lazy river, cascading pools, tipping bucket, and spinning gears.', 'This water table provides a rich environment for 31-33 month olds to engage in purposeful pouring, cause-and-effect play, and imaginative scenarios. The various water features encourage exploration and understanding of water flow. A solid ''buy'' for extended play.', 'The Bluey Beach Day Sand and Water Table offers multiple interactive elements like cascading pools, a tipping bucket, and spinning gears that encourage purposeful pouring and experimentation with water flow, aligning with the stage shift. The character play adds an imaginative dimension.', 'Requires dedicated outdoor space. Assembly may be required.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'Check whether the family already has a basic version. Upgrade only if this version solves a new job for 31-33 months.', 'Use only with close adult supervision around water.', 'good', ARRAY['https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/little-tikes-bluey-beach-day-sand-and-water-table/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_pouring_cups_and_water_lab', 6, 6, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for budgets', 'Big Jigs Measuring Cup with Cover', 'Big Jigs', NULL, 'https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/big-jigs-measuring-cup-with-cover/', NULL, '£1.99', NULL, NULL, 'Big Jigs — Big Jigs Measuring Cup with Cover', 'Basic measuring cup, good for introducing volume concepts at a low price point.', 'Basic measuring cup, good for introducing volume concepts at a low price point.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_pouring_cups_and_water_lab', 7, 7, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for small spaces', 'Gowi Toys Clear Watering Can', 'Gowi Toys', NULL, 'https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/gowi-toys-clear-watering-can/', NULL, '£6.99', NULL, NULL, 'Gowi Toys — Gowi Toys Clear Watering Can', 'Clear design allows children to observe water levels, good for early pouring practice.', 'Clear design allows children to observe water levels, good for early pouring practice.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_pouring_cups_and_water_lab', 8, 8, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for borrowing first', 'Gowi Watering Can', 'Gowi Toys', NULL, 'https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/gowi-watering-can/', NULL, '£5.50', NULL, NULL, 'Gowi Toys — Gowi Watering Can', 'Simple, durable watering can for basic pouring and water play.', 'Simple, durable watering can for basic pouring and water play.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_pouring_cups_and_water_lab', 9, 9, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for gifting', 'Green Toys Bubbling Mini Submarine Bath Toy', 'Green Toys', NULL, 'https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/green-toys-bubbling-mini-submarine-bath-toy/', NULL, '£5.50', NULL, NULL, 'Green Toys — Green Toys Bubbling Mini Submarine Bath Toy', 'Fun bath toy with pouring spout, made from recycled plastic, suitable for water exploration.', 'Fun bath toy with pouring spout, made from recycled plastic, suitable for water exploration.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_pouring_cups_and_water_lab', 10, 10, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for growing with them', 'Green Toys Sea Plane', 'Green Toys', NULL, 'https://www.adventuretoys.co.uk/green-toys-sea-plane/', NULL, '£18.50', NULL, NULL, 'Green Toys — Green Toys Sea Plane', 'Versatile toy for both air and water play, encouraging imaginative scenarios during water time.', 'Versatile toy for both air and water play, encouraging imaginative scenarios during water time.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_safe_step_up_stool_or_learning_tower', 1, 1, 'visible', true, false, 'Best for kitchen independence', 'Learning Tower, White', 'GLTC', 'GLTC', 'https://www.gltc.co.uk/products/learning-tower-white', NULL, '£85.00', 'in_stock', '18m+', 'A sturdy and stylish wooden learning tower, perfect for helping toddlers reach counter height safely.', 'This classic learning tower is ideal for 31-33 month olds eager to help in the kitchen. Its stable design allows for safe participation, fostering independence. Consider borrowing if space is limited.', 'At 31-33 months, toddlers seek more active roles. This tower provides the necessary height and security for them to engage in tasks like stirring or washing up, a clear progression from simpler steps.', 'Ensure adequate supervision, especially when first introducing the tower.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'Check whether the family already has a basic version. Upgrade only if this version solves a new job for 31-33 months.', 'Always supervise children when using a learning tower.', 'strong', ARRAY['https://www.gltc.co.uk/collections/learning-towers-step-stools']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_safe_step_up_stool_or_learning_tower', 2, 6, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for versatile use', 'The Original - Convertible Learning Tower', 'The Learning Tower Company', 'The Learning Tower Company', 'https://learningtowers.co.uk/products/the-original-convertible-learning-tower', NULL, '£109.99', 'in_stock', '18m+', 'A convertible learning tower that transforms into a table and chair, offering multiple uses.', 'This convertible tower is excellent for 31-33 month olds, providing a safe platform for tasks and then converting for play or meals. It grows with the child, offering great value.', 'The convertible feature extends its utility beyond just kitchen tasks, supporting the developing independence and varied interests of a 31-33 month old. This is more advanced than a simple step stool.', 'Ensure smooth conversion between modes and check stability in each configuration.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'Check whether the family already has a basic version. Upgrade only if this version solves a new job for 31-33 months.', 'Always supervise children when using a learning tower.', 'strong', ARRAY['https://learningtowers.co.uk/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_safe_step_up_stool_or_learning_tower', 3, 7, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for small spaces', 'The Original - Height Adjustable Folding Learning Tower', 'The Learning Tower Company', 'The Learning Tower Company', 'https://learningtowers.co.uk/products/the-original-height-adjustable-folding-learning-tower', NULL, '£159.99', 'in_stock', '18m+', 'A height-adjustable and foldable learning tower, ideal for easy storage in compact homes.', 'For 31-33 month olds in smaller homes, this folding and adjustable tower is a game-changer. It offers the safety and height needed for participation, then neatly stores away.', 'The folding mechanism addresses a common parent concern for space, while still providing the useful elevated and secure position for a 31-33 month old to engage in tasks, moving beyond a static step.', 'Check the ease and safety of the folding mechanism.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'Check whether the family already has a basic version. Upgrade only if this version solves a new job for 31-33 months.', 'Always supervise children when using a learning tower.', 'strong', ARRAY['https://learningtowers.co.uk/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_safe_step_up_stool_or_learning_tower', 4, 10, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for active toddlers', 'The Play Tower - Forest', 'The Learning Tower Company', 'The Learning Tower Company', 'https://learningtowers.co.uk/products/the-play-tower-forest', NULL, '£139.99', 'in_stock', '18m+', 'A learning tower with a fun forest design, encouraging imaginative play while helping.', 'This playful learning tower is perfect for 31-33 month olds who thrive on imaginative engagement. It makes helping a fun activity, aligning with their desire for ''real jobs''.', 'Beyond just elevation, this tower integrates play, making tasks more appealing for a 31-33 month old. It encourages sustained engagement, a step up from purely functional tools.', 'Consider if the design will remain appealing as the child grows.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'Check whether the family already has a basic version. Upgrade only if this version solves a new job for 31-33 months.', 'Always supervise children when using a learning tower.', 'strong', ARRAY['https://learningtowers.co.uk/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_safe_step_up_stool_or_learning_tower', 5, 14, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for durability and stability', 'The Tinker Tower - Premium', 'The Learning Tower Company', 'The Learning Tower Company', 'https://learningtowers.co.uk/products/the-tinker-tower-premium', NULL, '£274.99', 'in_stock', '18m+', 'A premium, robust learning tower designed for maximum stability and long-term use.', 'For families seeking a top-tier, exceptionally stable learning tower for their 31-33 month old, the Tinker Tower Premium is an excellent investment. It supports active participation with superior safety.', 'The premium build and enhanced stability cater to the increasing activity and confidence of a 31-33 month old, offering a secure platform for more complex tasks, surpassing basic models.', 'Higher price point; consider if the features justify the cost for your family''s needs.', 'buy', true, 'Thoughtful if age-fit and not already owned.', 'Check whether the family already has a basic version. Upgrade only if this version solves a new job for 31-33 months.', 'Always supervise children when using a learning tower.', 'strong', ARRAY['https://learningtowers.co.uk/']::text[], 'none'),
    ('cat_safe_step_up_stool_or_learning_tower', 6, 2, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for budgets', 'Learning Tower, Oatmeal', 'GLTC', NULL, 'https://www.gltc.co.uk/products/learning-tower-oatmeal', NULL, '£85.00', NULL, NULL, 'GLTC — Learning Tower, Oatmeal', 'Same as the white version, good alternative color.', 'Same as the white version, good alternative color.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
    ('cat_safe_step_up_stool_or_learning_tower', 7, 3, 'visible', true, true, 'Best for small spaces', 'Learning Tower, Ocean Blue', 'GLTC', NULL, 'https://www.gltc.co.uk/products/learning-tower-ocean-blue', NULL, '£85.00', NULL, NULL, 'GLTC — Learning Tower, Ocean Blue', 'Same as the white version, good alternative color.', 'Same as the white version, good alternative color.', NULL, 'borrow', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'emerging', ARRAY[]::text[], 'check_claim'),
